How to intelligently formulate a prob?
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Structured data
Organized, easy to analyze, time series, numeric

Unstructured data
Text, image, voice, videos, highly unorganized and contextual

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Structured data
- highly organized
- clearly defined var
- easy to mine
- numeric continuous var

Categorical data
- factor/ level/ class var

Mixed data
- numeric and categorical

Time series
- numeric with timestamps

Network data - social network, transport, websites, financial transaction
- highly organized nodes
- clearly defined links
- ez to mine and analyze
- nodes and connections

How to intelligently handle data?

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Unstructured data 
- Highly unorganized
- non-obvious var
- highly context-sensitive

Text - tweets
- words, phrases, emoticons

Image
- pixels & objects

Video
- image, frames, objects

Voice
- voice signals and waves

